This paper is about entity resolution in natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and evaluation metrics, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also mentions the use of datasets and text analysis techniques, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and computer vision (cs.CV) research.
